The default value for the `butter` function has `btype="low"`:
https://github.com/scipy/scipy/blob/98a210beff7230a4fad56b4e7ef1e9871145abcb/scipy/signal/_filter_design.py#L3376

However, the docstring in the same file says that `btype` should be one of `{'lowpass', 'highpass', 'bandpass', 'bandstop'}`:
https://github.com/scipy/scipy/blob/98a210beff7230a4fad56b4e7ef1e9871145abcb/scipy/signal/_filter_design.py#L3404-L3405

